Name: MOC 20497 Scripts
Description:
Sep 2016: Updated for Visual Studio 2015 and latest VSTS APIs.

This file contains files and setup scripts to be used by instructors deliver the official Microsoft training course 20497.

If you have any questions or concerns, please [url:contact me|mailto:richard@accentient.com]

Name: Fabrikam Fiber Website Installer
Description:
This installer is intended for provisioning a classroom computer, running IIS, with an instance of the Fabrikam Fiber website. The installer is very basic and makes these assumptions:

* Installs to c:\inetpub\wwwroot\fabrikam (by default)
* Creates a new site named _fabrikam_ running on port _1337_
* Uses the _DefaultAppPool_

+Important+: The DefaultAppPool must have "Enable 32-bit applications" set to true and run under a process identity with adequate permissions, such as _LocalSystem_.

After installing, you should be able to browse to http://localhost:1337 and interact with the website.

If you have any questions or concerns, please [url:contact me|mailto:richard@accentient.com]

Name: Fabrikam Fiber Source (Visual Studio 2015)
Description:
The Fabrikam Fiber Call Center solution and related projects.
